<s2>
<ptxt>
If clearance “a” is out of specification, select suitable shim which adjusts clearance “a” to specification and put it on bearing outer race.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Insert 0.2 mm (0.008 in.) feeler to know whether or not a shim fulfills specification quickly.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
