<s1>
<ptxt>
Place left case plate (2) inserting its end in groove of shift guide shaft (4), and then tighten new left case plate bolts (1) to specified torque.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
After tightening bolts, make sure that countershaft (3) can be rotated by hand with feeling certain load.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
